      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a very strong start and definitely brings out that sense of paranoia they had. Can you finish that last thought about Mississippi and then maybe expand on how they might discuss practical, everyday ways to maintain that \"order\" in the town? I'm looking for how they might talk about policing their own neighborhoods or dealing with people who don't follow the \"traditional\" social rules of the time.",
